  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609800/extras/1cfcb34862cd1cc959b442be0c2f7764.avif?t=1626386498\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br>Take control of Akinofa, a mysterious undead fish of green flames, in this difficult Roguelite shoot em' up! Beat as many enemies and get the highest score possible. Challenge your friends and the world Rankings!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609800/extras/01ba18ba5f9c82fa35e8f5a487370a62.poster.avif?t=1626386498\" width=600 height=294 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609800/extras/01ba18ba5f9c82fa35e8f5a487370a62.webm?t=1626386498\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609800/extras/01ba18ba5f9c82fa35e8f5a487370a62.mp4?t=1626386498\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Every action counts! Even if you don't finish a level, every coin you collect will be in your treasury to use for permanent upgrades.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Rogue-lite</strong> - With the gold, you collect you will be able to upgrade your ship's permanent stats on the Game Over screen. These upgrades are permanent and will help you with future playthroughs.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609800/extras/fd7bd73a8f2372d58dc86c20f43bc248.gif?t=1626386498\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609800/extras/fd7bd73a8f2372d58dc86c20f43bc248.poster.avif?t=1626386498\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Extremely challenging, yet rewarding gameplay<br></li><li> Beautifully designed retro-inspired graphics<br></li><li> Full controller support<br></li><li> Achievements<br></li><li> Online Rankings</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609800/extras/1cfcb34862cd1cc959b442be0c2f7764.avif?t=1626386498\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br>Take control of Akinofa, a mysterious undead fish of green flames, in this difficult Roguelite shoot em' up! Beat as many enemies and get the highest score possible. Challenge your friends and the world Rankings!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609800/extras/01ba18ba5f9c82fa35e8f5a487370a62.poster.avif?t=1626386498\" width=600 height=294 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609800/extras/01ba18ba5f9c82fa35e8f5a487370a62.webm?t=1626386498\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609800/extras/01ba18ba5f9c82fa35e8f5a487370a62.mp4?t=1626386498\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Every action counts! Even if you don't finish a level, every coin you collect will be in your treasury to use for permanent upgrades.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Rogue-lite</strong> - With the gold, you collect you will be able to upgrade your ship's permanent stats on the Game Over screen. These upgrades are permanent and will help you with future playthroughs.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609800/extras/fd7bd73a8f2372d58dc86c20f43bc248.gif?t=1626386498\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609800/extras/fd7bd73a8f2372d58dc86c20f43bc248.poster.avif?t=1626386498\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Extremely challenging, yet rewarding gameplay<br></li><li> Beautifully designed retro-inspired graphics<br></li><li> Full controller support<br></li><li> Achievements<br></li><li> Online Rankings</li></ul>",
